data.description: OPEN HOUSE SUNDAY 12/8 1-3pm ! Don't miss your opportunity to check out this unique tri-level home! Nestled in a quiet neighborhood of just a few homes, this residence boasts 3 bedrooms and 1 1/2 baths, offering the perfect blend of space and functionality for modern living. The main living area is open concept with lots of natural light, great for families and entertaining guests. The open design of the kitchen allows you to connect with guests in the the dining and living rooms, so you never miss any of the action! There is also a second living space (and second fireplace) that offers you even more possibilities for this home. Use it as a theater room, home gym, play room, swanky home bar or more! The possibilities are endless! The 3 bedrooms are tucked away on their own floor for added privacy. The large fenced in backyard is great for pets and kids, and with lots of trees behind the fence, it is quiet and tranquil. Don't miss the opportunity to make this tri-level gem your forever home. Schedule your viewing today and step into a life of comfort, style, and endless possibilities. Welcome home!
